            "title": "Acoustic monitoring reveals spatiotemporal occurrence of Nathusius’ pipistrelle at the southern North Sea during autumn migration",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Sander",
                    "lastName": "Lagerveld"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Tony",
